 \color{#00f}{\LARGE I} \equiv 3\int_{S}z^{4}\,\dd S=3a^{6}\int_{0}^{2\pi}\dd\phi \int_{0}^{\pi}\cos^{4}\pars{\theta}\sin\pars{\theta}\,\dd\theta =-6\pi a^{6}\int_{1}^{-1}t^{4}\,\dd t =\color{#00f}{\large{12\pi \over 5}\,a^{6}} 
